{"tid":1967113,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"泰國出現空心探熱槍　怎麼按都低於37度","createTime":"2020-04-10T16:20:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-10T17:44:50.000Z","uid":53379,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"259ed48aafb39b8eb25265f1b2bbdb166dd0b56a","tid":1967113,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T16:20:01.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">泰國出現空心額溫槍　怎麼按都低於37度</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n中國近來大舉向外援助試劑盒、口罩等防疫物資，想撇清武漢肺炎「禍害全球」的惡名，沒想到被受贈國踢爆「品質不佳」，甚至還有假額溫槍在泰國出現。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/zd-_B_G7NXOKpeKxV4kH53MfRLI=/412x243/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/2EUQKVTNEJOPRIWBLP7BV5Z3PM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2Fzd-_B_G7NXOKpeKxV4kH53MfRLI%3D%2F412x243%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2F2EUQKVTNEJOPRIWBLP7BV5Z3PM.jpg&h=39f950c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日前廣東東莞市顥峰電子科技有限公司老闆張懸東，揚言做假測溫槍賣給美國，「做點假貨賣過去，讓他們39度測出36.5度，讓他們越搞越多，看他美國還有多少人去別國傷人。」並且炫耀「不動一兵一卒，賺了錢又和平了世界。」遭到東莞當地政府人員已對他進行了批評教育。<br />\n<br />\n據泰國《Voice TV》報導，泰國警方8日指出，查獲兩名中國人走私假的武漢肺炎試劑到泰國，其中包含假的45000個武漢肺炎試劑，1200個額溫槍，350000個口罩，這些東西未經許可在曼谷販售。<br />\n<br />\n泰國也有網友在網路上分享買到的假額溫槍，拆開後發現裡面根本是空心的，不管怎麼按，跳出來的溫度都不會超過37度。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20200410/L3OH4UUP3M67DGMCNLVAE6ISSY/?utm_campaign=twad_social_apple.realtimenews&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR0XEarncyZ13dumES-TIwinF-krL6Y8jyBwlgzOuomApx4_554S0hXn5XA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200410%2FL3OH4UUP3M67DGMCNLVAE6ISSY%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dtwad_social_apple.realtimenews%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR0XEarncyZ13dumES-TIwinF-krL6Y8jyBwlgzOuomApx4_554